{"tid":1741232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳秋北率一眾市民到理大附近清理垃圾","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:42:51.000Z","uid":54800,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65b031b82a7dad216edde9684e829ff47fd7235d","tid":1741232,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"一批市民下午原先打算在紅隧九龍入口附近清理路障，遭警方拒絕他們進入封鎖線範圍，他們改為到香港體育館平台及附近清理垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n帶隊的工聯會會長吳秋北說，希望號召全港市民一起清潔香港，團結一致止暴制亂，對抗「黑色暴力」，呼籲群眾離開時沿途清理垃圾，協助盡快恢復香港原貌。<br />\n<br />\n對於立法會前主席曾鈺成，日前進入理大校園與示威者對話，吳秋北認為，觸犯法例的人應該主動自首。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你吳秋北又衝出黎抽水~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁把炮不如叫POPO撤走咪撚封哂D天橋呀行人墜道呀~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b55696d7bce5e8d02bbcfb602a1c37fe08f560d","tid":1741232,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"幫佢清晒叫popo快撚啲通車咪撚阻人收工"},{"pid":"8bd65d8052e2b1a7f750eb9dd888d8d77edfb3e8","tid":1741232,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"黎明行動 千祈唔好做呢啲行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc6b41a6e1e3f95464841f8119146c25a418cf1c","tid":1741232,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:15:37.000Z","msg":"暴動始祖話人暴動"},{"pid":"9a5954d6893fe31282b6be78c452d14675a5db30","tid":1741232,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"廢老準備食二噁英死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d1024e8be536451c782ce1fba721e2a2b9af8e","tid":1741232,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a5954d6893fe31282b6be78c452d14675a5db30","tid":1741232,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"廢老準備食二噁英死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces